===Leaving already, Little Gray...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Hysilens:''' Leaving already, Little Gray Fry? I made a batch of honey brew for the road. Since it's a special blend, I was hoping you'd give me your thoughts.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:{Choice} That's so thoughtful!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Thanks, that's so thoughtful of you!
:{Choice} I'll drink it all up!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll drink it all up!
:{Choice} Can I have some?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Can I have some?
::'''Hysilens:''' I've learned my lesson, so I've diluted this batch to be more human-friendly.
::{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' For this one, a Rift Valley nectar base with freshly squeezed moon fruit. It's got a sweet-yet-tart kick that's perfect for the little pink jellyfish.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' The green dragonfish always reminds me of the ancient ice of the deep seas. I thought a honey brew with mint and ginger might help clear his thoughts.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' I left the last few bottles unlabeled. I have a feeling you'll know who needs them most.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' There is one that warms you like the blazing sun, yet it's made from red-crowned sea cucumbers that only emerge at night. One sip, and you won't want the day to end.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' Another is a brown brew blended with nutritious minerals from the underwater mountains. It keeps for ages without losing a hint of its initial taste.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' For the last one, I've used the liquid stirred up by a school of silverfish dancing together. It's refreshingly balanced, and the aftertaste is a real treat.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:{Choice} Which is for me?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' So which brew is for me?
:{Choice} Himeko would love your recipes
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I bet Himeko would love to compare notes on these wild recipes of yours
::'''Hysilens:''' That would be great. I do hope she likes them.
::{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' For you, Little Gray Fry, this one holds a mix of blue stardust, shimmering gold flakes, and a sweet pink brew...
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' I call it "Memory of Amphoreus." Pour it into a glass, and it will dance with the glimmer of countless stars. Go on, give it a try.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' To our memories. May they forever shine as brightly as this drink, and may their sweetness be everlasting.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Voice message converted to text
:'''Hysilens:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 23 Hysilens 02.png|80px]]
}}
